#Privacy Policy for Bakery INC.

#Effective Date: 23.05.2023

This Privacy Policy governs the manner in which Bakery INC. collects, uses, maintains, and discloses information collected from users (referred to as "Users") of the Bakery INC. app (referred to as "the App").

Information Collection
Bakery INC. does not collect or store any personally identifiable information (PII) or personal data from its Users. We do not track, monitor, or gather any data that can be used to identify individual Users.

Non-Personal Information
Bakery INC. may collect non-personal information about Users whenever they interact with the App. This non-personal information may include technical details such as the device's operating system, device model, language preference, and other similar information. This data is collected solely for the purpose of improving the App's functionality and providing a better user experience.

Cookies and Similar Technologies
Bakery INC. does not use cookies or similar technologies to collect any information from Users.

Third-Party Services
Bakery INC. does not utilize any third-party services or integrate with any external platforms that would involve the collection or sharing of user data.

Security
Bakery INC. takes reasonable precautions to protect against the unauthorized access, use, alteration, or destruction of any non-personal information collected. However, please be aware that no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.

Children's Privacy
Bakery INC. does not knowingly collect any personal information from children under the age of 13. If you are a parent or guardian and believe that your child has provided personal information through the App, please contact us immediately, and we will take appropriate steps to remove that information from our records.

Changes to this Privacy Policy
Bakery INC. reserves the right to update or modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Users are encouraged to check this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes. By continuing to use the App, you acknowledge and agree to be bound by the updated Privacy Policy.

Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy or the practices of Bakery INC., please contact us at erturulkucukkaya@gmail.com.
